  dialogKedua_ID: Barang yang murah di sini bisa bernilai berlipat di tangan pembeli
    yang tepat. Aku harus memilih dengan cermat.
  dialogPertama_EN: Almost home... There are many local traders here selling goods
    at affordable prices.
  dialogKedua_EN: Goods that are cheap here can be worth much more in the hands of
    the right buyer. I need to choose carefully.
